== Agte ==

Agte is not a [[WP:RS]] source; pls see [[Talk:Joachim_Peiper#Agte]].

I suggest removing these two sentences attributed to him:

*Four of the Panzer IVs under Ribbentrop were destroyed by the time their position was overrun.{{sfn|Agte|2006|p=124}} 

*The three surviving tanks rode along with the advancing Soviet armour unnoticed, and they reported that they destroyed 14 Soviet tanks from close range.{{sfn|Agte|2006|p=125}} 

